---
import Author from '../Author.astro';
---

<div class='about-the-author py-4 border-b border-black/10 dark:border-white/10'>
	<h3 class='font-semibold uppercase mb-4 text-xs text-black/48 dark:text-white/48 tracking-[-0.12px]'>About the Author</h3>
	<Author picSize='md' />
	<div class='text-[14px] my-4 text-black/80 dark:text-white/80 leading-[1.43] tracking-[-0.224px]'>
		<p class='mb-3'>
			Koji is a software engineer with experiences building IoT system, Desktop application, and On-Device application. He is actively
			writing on{'new tech(mostly GenAI) and frontend stuff'}.
		</p>
		<p>
			He will be happy to work and collaborate in any project as a software engineer. His main stacks are React, TypeScript, Nodejs, and
			Python.
		</p>
	</div>
</div>
